<ul>
<li>Valid on NEW bookings made through our Lakes and Mountains programme between 4th and 30th June, travelling between 11th July and 29th August 2015.<br /><br /></li>
<li>Offer is applicable on our charter flights only departing on a Wednesday or Saturday from Birmingham, Bristol, Cambridge, Edinburgh, Gatwick, Leeds-Bradford, Manchester and Newcastle.<br /><br /></li>
